\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5b2cf62ece08116eda5168b9f3430c66fef677","tid":1623333,"uid":148934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:27:38.000Z","msg":"就算燒埋自己手足都唔割 成班左膠都on99"},{"pid":"094d52ddbc90bb25d8228c2ed2a6b3b54ed3b1bf","tid":1623333,"uid":325214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41011544bec1fa88580af9ab2d34a92773f3bf2e","tid":1623333,"uid":306180,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T22:32:16.000Z","msg":"重點係我地無搶掠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過都想大家諗諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚已經有mk同大媽執雞<br />\n當然佢地偷係佢地錯<br />\n但對家文宣一定無視同屈落手足度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大部份媒體會唔會咁樣詳細前因後過地報晒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只係唔想手足們既辛苦做左文宣炸彈<br />\n下次爆唔爆鋪、爆咩鋪、爆到點，希望手足諗清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:31:53.000Z","msg":"有人偷野咪諗辦法唔比佢偷嚕<br />\n淋花又花 打開哂包裝又好<br />\n有人偷野就唔裝修係咩邏輯？<br />\n即係民主有機會選到希特拉<br />\n所以民主就唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba427ca96bc1313e76656a0999b61f6b4d1aad57","tid":1623333,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:45:24.000Z","msg":"有一種方法可團結全港九成市民<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628196\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628196</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f1a45859c2ea117d767ee2aee580ee2383d59477","tid":1623333,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d615def5d352cc3efeffe54e7de4d959f779150","tid":1623333,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T