 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但和勇合一係成場運動既關鍵，兩樣一齊做唔撚得？講緊既係，拆鐵係唔撚會影響人權法，或所謂既民意，但對政權、運動係現時有最大既影響力"},{"pid":"af3ebfd629d6de8964a7f08994b0eb7db47d8227","tid":1623333,"uid":73419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:57:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"aba089bebf74b5d913bf8b0024d66f0a945a680f","tid":1623333,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead298fdc5336170b65595c3dbc5cf0b1fb96b40","tid":1623333,"uid":159762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:56:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港警察濫權實錄資料庫</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline&d=Bs0XXOgOekCAei%2FiISrrFh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=ed7c4051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有英文同日文版 大家落力share俾更多外國人睇！！</span>"},{"pid":"1d7e3adbb54a1c7f04acadaeff13770c62e4df86","tid":1623333,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:40:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08756be211cfc2c3d4b24caacffaf13b99f9f8b0","tid":1623333,